document_data.History:
Jhessail was a high-ranking member of the [[Knights of the Black Fist]].
She exemplified the corruption and cruelty that was synonymous with organization and prospered.
In [[1489 DR]] Jhessail lead a rebellion against [[Vorgansharax]] but was betrayed by her fellow officers and captured.{{Cite adventurers league/Escape from Phlan|7}}
She was freed by an adventuring party hired by the resistance  and managed to escape [[Phlan]].

Around [[1492 DR]], Jhessail led an alliance to reclaim Phlan.{{Cite adventurers league/Reclamation of Phlan|6}}
